DESC:
```
Carrying no physical form, Echoes exist merely as sound-based entities. They carry the voices of souls that have ceased to exist.
Capable of traveling far beyond their attached NulGraven Site, they can silently stalk prey or harass them. From calls into the darkness, cries for help, or screams of pain, echo caradels are a nightmare to deal with alone.

If you stay silent, they should eventually get bored and leave.
Shouting back is effective at scaring them off faster.
Although, if their whispers only get louder after yelling, remain silent at all costs.
```

